result.name: https-www-wirral-gov-uk-about-council-budgets-and-spending-payments-suppliers-and-agents
result.notes:
This dataset provides information on Wirral Councils spend over £500. Details are provided to meet the Local Government Transparency Code 2015. 

The payment date for credit card payments gives the actual date of spend, the payment of the statement may be later.
result.title: Wirral Expenditure Exceeding £500
